### Footnotes

<span id="fn_26"></span>[33:360](0748.htm#fr_26.md) : The remarks
accompanying the plan reproduced on [Pl. LXXXI](pl081.htm#img_pl081.md),
No. 2 are as follows: Above, to the left: "*in* a *angholo stia la
guardia de la sstalla*" (in the angle *a* may be the keeper of the
stable). Below are the words "*strada dabosa*" (road to Amboise),
parallel with this "*fossa br 40*" (the moat 40 braccia) fixing the
width of the moat. In the large court surrounded by a portico "*in terre
No.--Largha br.80 e lugha br 120*." To the right of the castle is a
large basin for aquatic sports with the words "*Giostre colle nave cioe
li giostra li stieno sopra le na*" (Jousting in boats that is the men
are to be in boats). J. P. R.

